| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4793 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d76631ba-8806-53c4-aaf8-cc12f4124bbd"
